	)
	(text "WiFi Communication\nADC2 Unusable: GPIO11-21 ADC disabled\nADC1 Usable: GPIO1-10 ADC enabled\nPrioritising the fast FOC loop means\nencoders are communicating with slave\ninstead of master.\nUART for communication between MCUs due \nto asynchronous nature \nFor safety, MCU watchdog timer incase error"
